# Domain + routes sync

New domain/sub-domain, `*.container.ts`, `*.routes.ts`, or `src/routes.ts` wiring? Run **[domain-generator](../skills/domain-generator/SKILL.md)**; for routes also **[route-schema-doc-guard](../skills/route-schema-doc-guard/SKILL.md)** + **[route-catalog](../skills/route-catalog/SKILL.md)**. Full chains: `new-domain` / `route-change` in `agent-os/skills/chains.json`.
